# Dialogue System Rules

## GDScript
- All dialogue loaded from JSON files under `res://data/dialogue/`
- NPC personality types must be from the `NpcPersonality` enum
- Stat checks must respect MarketMood modifier
- Every dialogue outcome must emit `dialogue_ended` with the NPC id and outcome string

## JSON Dialogue Files
- Required top-level keys: `npc_id`, `quest_id`, `start_node`, `nodes`
- Every node needs: `speaker`, `text`, `options` array
- Options need at minimum: `text`, `next` (node id or "end")
- Stat effects go in `stat_effects` dict with valid stat names only
- `mood_variants` optional per node (keys: "crash", "boom", "stable")
- `karma` values: positive = ethical choice, negative = exploitative
- Fight outcomes use `"outcome": "fight"`, flee uses `"outcome": "fled"`
- Faction encounters must include `faction_id` at the top level
